Class ConfigurableDuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.Abhigya.core.util.Duration
      • me.Abhigya.core.util.configurable.duration.ConfigurableDuration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable, Loadable, Saveable, Validable

    public class ConfigurableDuration
extends Duration
implements Configurable
    Represents a Duration that is 'Configurable' because can be loaded from/saved on a ConfigurationSection.
